g',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(120,1,'2015-04-21 15:19:48','2015-04-21 08:19:48','* A subsidiary of the Airports Corporation of Vietnam (ACV), Hanoi Ground Services (HGS) is now offering a full range of ground handling services to a diverse customer base of international and domestic airlines at Noibai International Airport (HAN), the capital of Vietnam.\r\n\r\n* Established in July 2007, HGS has been developed and confidential to be a reliable ground services provider to deliver excellent services in compliance with the industry standards of International Air Transport Association, applicable regulations of the State, CAAV and customized requirement of customer airlines.\r\n\r\n* With experience of 7 years in ground handling, HGS have obtained and successfully renewed the ISO 9001 quality management certification and successfully registered the industry ISAGO (IATA Safety Audits for Ground Operations).','Introduction','','inherit','open','open','','70-revision-v1','','','2015-04-21 15:19:48','2015-04-21 08:19:48','',70,'http://128.199.124.217/wordpress/70-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(122,1,'2015-04-21 15:30:29','2015-04-21 08:30:29','','Tuvnord','','inherit','open','open','','tuvnord','','','2015-04-21 15:30:29','2015-04-21 08:30:29','',0,'http://128.199.124.217/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Tuvnord.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(123,1,'2015-04-21 15:31:33','2015-04-21 08:31:33','','','','inherit','open','open','','logo-isago','','','2015-04-21 15:31:38','2015-04-21 08:31:38','',0,'http://128.199.124.217/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Logo-ISAGO.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(124,1,'2015-04-21 15:41:37','2015-04-21 08:41:37','','Tuvnord','','inherit','open','open','','tuvnord-2','','','2015-04-21 15:41:37','2015-04-21 08:41:37','',0,'http://128.199.124.217/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Tuvnord1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(125,1,'2015-04-21 15:46:04','2015-04-21 08:46:04','','','','inherit','open','open','','acv1','','','2015-04-21 15:46:08','2015-04-21 08:46:08','',0,'http://128.199.124.217/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/acv1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(126,1,'2015-04-21 15:47:18','2015-04-21 08:47:18','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>THNG BO</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>V VIC TUYN DNG LAO NG</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CNG TY PHC V MT T H NI </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>a ch: Cng hng khng quc t Ni Bi </strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>X Ph Minh, Huyn Sc Sn, Thnh ph H Ni</strong></p>\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>TUYN DNG LAO NG CC V TR V IU KIN D TUYN C TH NH SAU:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Chc danh nhn vin phc v hnh khch + Nhn vin iu hnh, ti liu v hng dn cht xp:</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n- Gii tnh: Nam, n <em>(u tin nam gii)</em>\r\n\r\n-  tui: + Nam khng qu 30 tui\r\n\r\n+ N khng qu 28 tui\r\n\r\n- Trnh  chuyn mn: Tt nghip ph thng trung hc tr ln\r\n\r\n- Trnh  ting Anh: TOEIC ti thiu 450 im hoc tng ng.\r\n\r\n- Trnh  tin hc: S dng thnh tho tin hc vn phng\r\n\r\n- u tin ng vin bit thm ngoi ng khc\r\n\r\n- Sc khe: + Sc khe tt\r\n\r\n+ Chiu cao: Nam t 1,66 m tr ln, N t 1,56 m tr ln\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">H s d tuyn gm:</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>n d tuyn ghi r chc danh d tuyn, kinh nghim bn thn, qu trnh cng tc (nu c).</li>\r\n	<li>S yu l lch (dn nh 4x6) c xc nhn ca chnh quyn a phng.</li>\r\n	<li>Giy khm sc khe (trong thi hn 03 thng tnh t ngy np h s) do cc c quan y t c thm quyn cp.</li>\r\n	<li>Bn sao (cng chng) giy khai sinh, Bng ph thng trung hc v cc vn bng khc (nu c) + bng im, chng ch c lin quan, chng minh nhn dn, h khu.</li>\r\n	<li>Giy xc nhn ca Cng an ni thng tr v nhn thn, hnh kim (trong thi hn 03 thng tnh t ngy np h s).</li>\r\n	<li>02 phong b c dn tem, ghi r h tn, a ch, in thoi lin lc v 02 nh 4x6</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Thi gian, a im nhn h s:</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Thi gian: Ngy 25/04/2015 (Gi hnh chnh)</li>\r\n	<li>a im Tng 5, Ta nh a nng 169, Nguyn Ngc V, Trung Ha, Cu Giy, H Ni</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Ghi ch:</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Thi gian thi tuyn d kin: Tun u thng 05/2015</li>\r\n	<li>Cc thng tin lin quan n thi tuyn c ng trn Website ca Cng ty Phc v mt t H Ni: <a href=\"http://www.hgs.com.vn/\">hgs.com.vn</a> hoc <a href=\"http://www.hgs.vn/\">www.hgs.vn</a>; Thng tin chi tit lin quan lin h theo s in thoi: 043. 5844110.</li>\r\n	<li>Khng hon tr h s  np i vi ng vin khng trng tuyn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"> <strong>GIM C</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong> </strong><em>( k)</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><em> Bi Tun Anh</em></strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Recruiment Notice 2015','','publish','closed','closed','','thong-tin-tuyen-dung-2015','','','2015-04-22 10:24:27','2015-04-22 03:24:27','',0,'http://128.199.124.217/?p=126',0,'post','',0),(127,1,'2015-04-21 15:47:18','2015-04-21 08:47:18','.........................................','Thng tin tuyn dng 2015','','inherit','open','open','','126-revision-v1','','','2015-04-21 15:47:18','2015-04-21 08:47:18','',126,'http://128.199.124.217/126-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(128,1,'2015-04-21 15:53:54','2015-04-21 08:53:54','','hx','','publish','closed','closed','','hx','','','2015-04-21 16:48:34','2015-04-21 09:48:34','',0,'http://128.199.124.217/?post_type=slides&#038;p=128',0,'slides','',0),(129,1,'2015-04-21 15:53:44','2015-04-21 08:53:44','','hx1','','inherit','open','open','','hx1','','','2015-04-21 15:53:44','2015-04-21 08:53:44','',128,'http://128.199.124.217/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/hx1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(130,1,'2015-04-21 15:58:47','2015-04-21 08:58:47','<a href=\"http://128.199.124.217/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/chinhsach.png\"><im